Ok, forget about FZ beginning to walk off then.

::FZ::

FZ nods at the explanation, looking at Perndabot to see if he had a 
different story. Perndabot didn't.

"Allright." he says, turning to Nue'e and Biomass, "I suppose you're 
here to join, and not to fight, right?"
